00:04:34.183 --> 00:04:35.532
Legende su istinite.

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:37.384
Neko će morati da ode!

00:04:37.534 --> 00:04:38.084
Majko...

00:04:38.367 --> 00:04:40.230
Motunui je raj!

00:04:40.443 --> 00:04:42.268
Zašto bi neko želeo da ode bilo gde?

00:05:19.251 --> 00:05:21.585
Iš!

00:05:55.888 --> 00:06:01.955
<i>Oči su ti tako radoznale</i>

00:06:02.055 --> 00:06:08.423
<i>Srce ti je nevin ratnik</i>

00:06:08.723 --> 00:06:14.357
<i>Najdraža moja</i>

00:06:14.557 --> 00:06:21.157
<i>Dobićeš zadatak</i>

00:06:21.291 --> 00:06:27.258
<i>Neka preleti preko tebe</i>

00:06:27.591 --> 00:06:34.325
<i>Sloboda koju osećaš</i>

00:06:34.392 --> 00:06:39.993
<i>I tvoje misli</i>

00:06:40.093 --> 00:06:46.360
<i>Naša malena</i>

00:06:47.393 --> 00:06:53.294
<i>Došla si</i>

00:06:53.827 --> 00:06:59.528
<i>Mlada devojko</i>

00:07:02.156 --> 00:07:02.983
Moana!

00:07:08.829 --> 00:07:16.896
<i>Oči su ti tako radoznale</i>

