i niko ne odlazi!
Pa ću i ja ostati.

00:11:32.520 --> 00:11:34.323
Moj dom i narod pored mene.

00:11:34.539 --> 00:11:36.385
I kada mislim na budućnost.

00:11:36.402 --> 00:11:38.624
Tu smo svi.

00:11:38.652 --> 00:11:40.183
Vodiću ih.

00:11:40.559 --> 00:11:42.526
Narod će me voditi.

00:11:42.776 --> 00:11:44.669
Gradićemo budućnost zajedno.

00:11:44.695 --> 00:11:46.644
Jer smo tu.

00:11:46.667 --> 00:11:48.589
Jer svaki put te vodi...

00:11:48.624 --> 00:11:50.824
tu gde si.

00:11:50.860 --> 00:11:54.403
Naći ćeš sreću...
- Tu gde si.

00:11:54.539 --> 00:11:57.988
Tu gde si...

00:12:01.715 --> 00:12:05.043
Svaki put kada pada liša, krov prokišnjava
bez obzira koliko lišća stavljam.

00:12:05.084 --> 00:12:05.794
Popravljeno!

00:12:05.908 --> 00:12:07.275
Veži lišće!

00:12:09.778 --> 00:12:11.358
Vetar je pomerio stub.

00:12:12.771 --> 00:12:13.945
Ovo je dobra svinjetina!

00:12:16.757 --> 00:12:18.050
Oh, mislim...

00:12:18.248 --> 00:12:18.934
Ne, nisam...

00:12:19.302 --> 00:12:21.826
Šta, zovu me, moram da...

00:12:22.381 --> 00:12:22.892
Ćao!

00:12:25.985 --> 00:12:27.311
Dobro ti ide.

00:12:27.362 --> 00:12:28.614
Da li je gotovo?

00:12:30.871 --> 00:12:32.038
Blizu.

00:12:46.751 --> 00:12:48.644
Pitam se u vezi tog pileta.

00:12:48.770 --> 00:12:49.960
Jede kamen!

00:12:49.985 --> 00:12:55.070
Mislim da mu nedostaje
osnovna inteligencija za sve.

00:12:55.404 --> 00:12:56.746
